sources.description:
Trapped in the maze of a murderous racket!
A pseudo-patriotic hate group sends a woman to distract a New York assistant district attorney keen on taking them down.

Original title: Jigsaw (1949) AKA: Gun Moll

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/0AEhtHqdCok


This film is available with subtitles in many language options.

Director: Fletcher Markle
Writers: Fletcher Markle, Vincent McConnor 
Stars: Franchot Tone, Jean Wallace, Myron McCormick, Marlene Dietrich
Genres: Classics, Crime, Drama, Film-Noir
Budget: $400,000 (estimated)
